Luck & Omens
"My luck has been terrible lately. I feel like the Divines have turned their backs on me. I need a good omen, something to turn my fortunes around."
Offer a lucky charm (a physical item), perform a small blessing, or succeed on a Guile roll to invent a convincing good omen.
17
